GMDNPTCodeForm is a Form
    is primary
    title is "GMDN_Term"
    Layout
        single column
            visible when (RecordExists)
                paragraph
                    ItemGroup
                        display as text
                GMDNPTCode
                    label is "Code"
                    display as text
            visible when (not RecordExists)
                paragraph
                    ItemGroup
                GMDNPTCode
                    label is "Code"
            Name
        two column distributed
            Definition
                use text area of 8 lines
        single column
            Active
